title: Bob Wills and The Texas Playboys - Snader Transcriptions Video
description:
Bob Wills & The Texas Playboys - Snader Transcriptions video in mp4 format.

These 1951 Snader Telescriptions show a nervous looking Bob Wills singing and playing the music that he had performed since the 1930s. Joe "Jody" Holley is the second fiddle player and Bobby Koefer is on steel guitar. Joe Andrews main vocalist. Carolina Cotton vocals. Monte Mountjoy on the drums. Joe Frank Furguson on base and vocals. Skeeter Elkins on piano.  Please note guitarist Cotton Whittington, a lefty who played a guitar strung for a right hand player
